## Docker commands used to run the application
docker run --name techtrendscontainer --restart always -d -p 3111:3111 techtrends:latest

m95851@DWP-TK6FL7hihfC MINGW64 ~
$ docker ps
CONTAINER ID   IMAGE               COMMAND           CREATED        STATUS        PORTS                                         NAMES
cf626a137855   techtrends:latest   "python app.py"   39 hours ago   Up 39 hours   0.0.0.0:3111->3111/tcp, [::]:3111->3111/tcp   techtrendscontainer



